OL,3,C'My mum has become my patient': The
OL,4,Cunpaid carers calling for recognition
OL,6,F"I do not feel valued in anyway, shape
OL,7,Fof form.
OL,9,F"I do not like anything about this
OL,10,Fsystem, because they don't care about
OL,11,Fus."
OL,13,FCarers receive a government allowance
OL,14,Fof #81.90 a week.
OL,16,FBut for many it is a round-the-clock
OL,17,Fresponsibility.
